data.description: Charming 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom, all-brick ranch home in serene Kellwood Subdivision! This home features a sizeable living room partially open to the dining room and kitchen, with brilliant engineered hardwood adorning the floors of all three areas. The kitchen boasts ample counter-space and beautiful white cabinetry, as well as a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances (including a dishwasher), a tiled backsplash, recessed lighting, and French doors leading to the back patio. Beautiful engineered hardwood flooring continues through the hallway and into the sizeable primary suite, which itself features a walk-in closet in the bedroom and a stunning recently-updated vanity in the attached primary half bathroom. The home's full bathroom boasts ceramic tile floors and a gorgeous tiled with a glass door. Two more bedrooms and a laundry/mud room complete the interior of the home. The exterior of the home features tasteful, well-kept landscaping in the front, as well as a large, sprawling, shaded backyard with a full privacy fence, providing an ideal space for family barbecues or entertaining summer guests. A convenient outdoor shedlocated at the rear of the backyardprovides extra storage space, and completes the property. This is an approved Short Sale at the list price.
